trans-unit.source: Represents the context for the validation of an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa o contexto para a validação de um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" />.
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the target of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" />.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" /> class, while initializing the <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the target of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" />, ao inicializar o <see cref="T:System.Type" /> do destino do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the target of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Type" /> do destino do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> representado por esta instância.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> of the target of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> do destino do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> representado por esta instância.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" /> class, initializing the <see cref="T:System.Type" /> and the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> of the target of the bind represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.BindValidationContext" />, inicializando o <see cref="T:System.Type" /> e o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> do destino da associação representada por esta instância.

trans-unit.source: Is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: É uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> of the target of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AccessTypes" /> do destino do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityBind" /> representado por esta instância.
